       Name: Read Opponent
       Kind: Skill
     Target: TAR_CHAR_OFFENSIVE
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 8
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: TRUE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: You lose your read on your opponent.
Acquisition:
   - Sentinel: level 10
Description:
   Read Opponent is one of the Sentinel's foundational analytical techniques.
   The Sentinel studies their target's fighting style, identifying patterns,
   tendencies, and weaknesses over the course of a few exchanges. Once a
   read is established, the Sentinel gains improved accuracy and damage
   against that specific opponent.

   The benefit accumulates as long as the Sentinel maintains engagement with
   the read target. The information gathered — stance preferences, telegraphed
   attacks, habitual defenses — remains valid until the target significantly
   changes their approach or the Sentinel disengages. Read Opponent is the
   cornerstone of the Sentinel's adaptive combat philosophy: every fight
   begins with observation and ends with exploitation of identified patterns.
*******************************************************************************
